%^BOLD%^-=%^MAGENTA%^Travel Domain%^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^=-%^RESET%^

Those with the travel domain are masters of motion, 
as little as moving themselves from one room to the 
next without doors to as impressive as creating a 
portal through which to transport an entire group.

The travel domain contains the following spells:
Faithful Mount (3rd), Pass Portal (6th), Create Portal (8th)

%^CYAN%^Deities%^RESET%^: Callamir, Lysara

%^BOLD%^Please see individual help files for an explanation of what each spell does.%^RESET%^
     